    "Journal entries are stored locally and can sync through your iCloud private database when enabled. Sync changes apply on next app launch. Export creates a full JSON backup you can keep." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Journal entries are stored locally and can sync through your iCloud private database when enabled. Sync changes apply on next app launch. Export creates a full JSON backup you can keep."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "日记默认存储在本地，启用后可通过你的 iCloud 私有数据库同步。同步更改会在下次启动应用时生效。导出可生成完整 JSON 备份供你保存。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
